Package: portoptim
Title: Portfolio optimization with R
Type: Package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Antoniya Shivarova
Maintainer: Antoniya Shivarova <an.shivarova@gmail.com>
Description: 
  The `portoptim` package provides tools for portfolio optimization using R. 
  It includes functions for constructing and analyzing efficient portfolios, 
  calculating risk metrics, and visualizing portfolio performance. Designed 
  for both academic and practical applications, the package aims to simplify 
  the process of portfolio management and optimization.
